csupₛ_empty:
#print csupₛ_empty /-
@[simp]
theorem csupₛ_empty : supₛ (∅ : set ℤ) = 0 :=
  dif_neg (by simp)
#align cSup_empty csupₛ_empty
-/
cSup_of_not_bdd_above:
theorem cSup_of_not_bdd_above {s : set ℤ} (h : ¬BddAbove s) : supₛ s = 0 :=
  dif_neg (by simp [h])
#align cSup_of_not_bdd_above cSup_of_not_bdd_above
cSup_mem:
theorem cSup_mem {s : set ℤ} (h1 : s.nonempty) (h2 : BddAbove s) : supₛ s ∈ s :=
  by
  convert (greatest_of_bdd _ (Classical.choose_spec h2) h1).2.1
  exact dif_pos ⟨h1, h2⟩
#align cSup_mem cSup_mem
cSup_eq_greatest_of_bdd:

theorem cSup_eq_greatest_of_bdd {s : set ℤ} [decidable_pred (· ∈ s)] (b : ℤ) (Hb : ∀ z ∈ s, z ≤ b)
    (Hinh : ∃ z : ℤ, z ∈ s) : supₛ s = greatestOfBdd b Hb Hinh :=
  by
  convert dif_pos _ using 1
  · convert coe_greatest_of_bdd_eq _ (Classical.choose_spec (⟨b, Hb⟩ : BddAbove s)) _
  · exact ⟨Hinh, b, Hb⟩
#align cSup_eq_greatest_of_bdd cSup_eq_greatest_of_bdd

cInf_mem:
theorem cInf_mem {s : set ℤ} (h1 : s.nonempty) (h2 : BddBelow s) : infₛ s ∈ s :=
  by
  convert (least_of_bdd _ (Classical.choose_spec h2) h1).2.1
  exact dif_pos ⟨h1, h2⟩
#align cInf_mem cInf_mem
cInf_eq_least_of_bdd:
theorem cInf_eq_least_of_bdd {s : set ℤ} [decidable_pred (· ∈ s)] (b : ℤ) (Hb : ∀ z ∈ s, b ≤ z)
    (Hinh : ∃ z : ℤ, z ∈ s) : infₛ s = leastOfBdd b Hb Hinh :=
  by
  convert dif_pos _ using 1
  · convert coe_least_of_bdd_eq _ (Classical.choose_spec (⟨b, Hb⟩ : BddBelow s)) _
  · exact ⟨Hinh, b, Hb⟩
#align cInf_eq_least_of_bdd cInf_eq_least_of_bdd
